        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "refactor: add embedded run session target seam",
        "body": "## What\n\nAdds storage-neutral session target and transaction-boundary seams over the current file-backed implementation for the Path 3 session/transcript SQLite migration stack.\n\n## Why\n\nSQLite needs caller-visible session/transcript mutations to be operation-sized, not composed from separate transcript file work plus `session_entries.entry_json` updates. This keeps the current file-backed behavior while giving the SQLite implementation one backend-owned transaction for each logical mutation.\n\n## Changes\n\n- Adds embedded run target resolver\n- Migrates embedded helper callers\n- Adds compaction checkpoint store boundary\n- Moves checkpoint branch/restore entry writes\n- Adds parent-session fork entry boundary\n- Covers subagent, reply, consult forks\n\n## Testing\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/gateway/session-compaction-checkpoints.test.ts src/gateway/server.sessions.compaction.test.ts src/gateway/server.sessions.permissions-hooks.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/subagent-spawn.context.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/session.test.ts src/talk/agent-consult-runtime.test.ts src/gateway/session-compaction-checkpoints.test.ts src/gateway/server.sessions.compaction.test.ts src/gateway/server.sessions.permissions-hooks.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs src/auto-reply/reply/session-fork.ts src/auto-reply/reply/session.ts src/auto-reply/reply/session.test.ts src/agents/subagent-spawn.ts src/agents/subagent-spawn.runtime.ts src/agents/subagent-spawn.context.test.ts src/agents/subagent-spawn.test-helpers.ts src/agents/openclaw-tools.subagents.sessions-spawn.test-harness.ts src/talk/agent-consult-runtime.ts src/talk/agent-consult-runtime.test.ts src/gateway/session-compaction-checkpoints.ts src/gateway/server-methods/sessions.ts src/gateway/session-compaction-checkpoints.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.test.src.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/test-src.tsbuildinfo`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\n\nKnown unrelated proof blocker: `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.core.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core.tsbuildinfo` currently stops on `src/agents/cli-runner/prepare.ts(83,3): error TS6196: 'RunCliAgentParams' is declared but never used.`\n\n## Downstream\n\nSQLite adapters should implement checkpoint branch/restore and parent-session fork as backend-owned transactions that copy/select transcript rows and update `session_entries.entry_json` together. No new compaction checkpoint schema is introduced here.\n\nRefs #88838\n",
